# Employee Management System (EMS)

A backend system built with .NET 9, ASP.NET Core Web API, and Clean Architecture.

---

## Technology Stack

-Backend: .NET 9, ASP.NET Core Web API
-ORM: Entity Framework Core
-Main Database: MSSQL
-Log Database: PostgreSQL
-Authentication: JWT Bearer Token
-Authorization: Database-driven RBAC
-Validation: FluentValidation

---

## Project Structure

EmployeeManagementSystem/
??? EmployeeManagement.Domain          # Core entities, enums
??? EmployeeManagement.Application     # Business logic, DTOs, Services
??? EmployeeManagement.Persistence     # MSSQL, EF Core, Repositories
??? EmployeeManagement.Infrastructure  # JWT, Password Hashing, PostgreSQL Logs
??? EmployeeManagement.Shared          # Response models, Exceptions
??? EmployeeManagement.Configuration   # DI Registration, Middleware
??? EmployeeManagement.WebAPI          # Controllers, Program.cs

---

